<h2 id="Getting_started"><i class="fa fa-road fa-fw"></i>&nbsp;Getting started</h2>
Anyone is welcome to edit or create pages on this wiki.

Gentoo wiki contributors encourage beginners to consult the [[Help:Contents|Help page]] before making edits. It also links to the [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Contents MediaWiki User's Guide] which contains information on how to use wiki software.

If there is something we can improve please let us know on the [[Gentoo_Wiki:Feedback|Feedback page]].

For any questions ''related to using or editing the wiki'', you can always join our {{IRC|gentoo-wiki|mode=webchat}} IRC channel on Freenode or email us at [mailto:wiki@gentoo.org wiki@gentoo.org].

'''Please note''': For general Gentoo support, please get in touch with our [https://www.gentoo.org/support/ support community] instead. General support is ''not'' provided via the wiki.

